                            <div>
                              <p>Accountants are in high demand globally, with the Big Four (Price Waterhouse Cooper, Ernst &amp; Young, Deloitte, and KPMG) among the largest employers of graduates. In China, the profession continues to grow steadily. At present there are over 300,000 people working in the industry.</p>
                              <p>Globally there are many different qualifications that students can take to become practicing accountants; we will be looking at three, ACCA, CPA (US) and CPA (China). There are some significant differences between the three, and the best qualification to take depends entirely upon where you wish to practice as an accountant.</p>
                              &nbsp;<a class="l-cta cta" title="Search" href="/en/study-programs?icsregion=all&amp;icsdiscipline=economics,_accounting_and_finance&amp;#coursetool">Find an accounting course</a>&nbsp;
